item.dc:creator: @the_bank the bank
item.description:
@the_bank wrote:

[quote=“Greeny, post:10, topic:223150”]CFParse is easy to get hold of, this nigger just wanted to advertise his site.[/quote]Err, no?

This “nigger” wanted to make a helpful post. I have no need and no want to advertise my site, and I was not advertising it at all, I simply uploaded it there so it is guaranteed it won’t go down and no wait times for downloads.

Secondly, CFParse is not easy to get ahold of. Since it was discontinued by IBM, you can only get it from people willing to upload it. Needless to say, most people are too lazy or just plain assholes and won’t do so.
